nodes.text: Keerag was a male Trandoshan who worked as a bounty hunter, along with his brother, Currsk. After the Human Deggar Feps angered the Hutt Sonnos, Feps attempted to travel from the planet of Nal Hutta to its moon, Nar Shaddaa, by gaining passage aboard the starship Lost Lady. Keerag and Currsk also took up places on the ship, planning to find and kill Feps.
